title: Doctor Who (seasons 1-9 complete)
description:
season 1 (2005, 9th Dr) --- season 9 (2015, 12th Dr) inclusive.
All episodes and specials
see     https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_Doctor_Who_serials

not...
Supplemental episodes, web-episodes, amazon/itune minis, internet broadcasts, nor Prequels, etc

Enjoy.

Half are in the superiour MKV container: V) x264, 2Mbps.  A)aac,2chan,48kHz     Eg) 960x720 500MB
Half are in the old AVI format: V) xvid, 1Mbps. A) mp3, 128Kbps   Eg) 640x350ish 380MB
360-750MB per episode. Typically 720p.

None use the DRM-supporter, AssBanditApple, out-of-date mp4 container.
Thanks to all uploaders for the originals
